Import scoring notes checking inter-rater repeatability

Source: R/import_inter-rater_scores.R
import_interrater_scores.Rd

Imports, formats data into proper types and calculates the final reproducibility score.

import_interrater_scores()

Value

A [tibble::tibble()] object of reproducibility score notes formatted for use in analysis and manuscript preparation

Examples

notes <- import_notes()
pander::pander(head(notes))
